body.p: This model is according to the paper Reduced-order modeling of biochemical networks: application to the GTPase-cycle signalling module by Maurya et al 2006.The figure 4c is reproduced by Copasi 4.0.19 (development) .It is three-dimensional logarithmic plots show the output of simulations of Z at various concentrations of R and GAP.
